getExcessReserveBalance(address,address,.notice: Retrieves the excess reserve balance of a token in the vault.

getIntrinsicMinimumValue(address).notice: Retrieves the intrinsic minimum value of the vault.

getLiquidityRatio(address,address).notice: Calculates the liquidity ratio of the vault.

getPositionCapacity(address,address,(int.notice: Calculates the capacity of a liquidity position.

getTotalSupply(address,bool).notice: Retrieves the total supply of a token in the pool.

getUnderlyingBalances(address,address,ui.notice: Retrieves the underlying balances of a liquidity position.
